# fcc_wikipedia_viewer
This is a Wikipeida viewer which searches through Wikipedia for the search term entered by the user and shows the resuts along with a description. The user can also open a random Wikipedia article by clicking on 'Random' button.<br>
The apps works in the browser using frontend technologies only. The designing is done using CSS and the functionality is provided using jQuery.
A <a href="https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/API:Main_page">Wikipedia API</a> from MediaWiki is being used to get the search results from Wikipedia. 

